metadata.name: The magic Formula of nine stars
metadata.description:
Accompanied by a sharp pain in the head, Jiang Xuan suddenly woke up.



"This is..." He found himself in a world of stars.



The endless star fields are scattered all over the place.



Nine of them were so bright that they overshadowed all the stars around them.



They slowly run, there seems to be a certain kind of attraction between each other, pulling each other.
